{"word":"πολεμιστής","slug":"πολεμιστής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πολεμιστής</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:πολεμίζω'><el>πολεμίζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a warrior, combatant</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><el>π. ἵππος</el> <i>a war-horse, charger</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}